p: Other common signs and symptoms include headache; fatigue; muscle pain (myalgia); distal joint swelling; cutaneous manifestations, such as macular or maculopapular rash; and gastrointestinal tract affections, such as nausea, vomiting, and abdominal pain [ 93, 94]. Less frequently, ocular manifestations can occur, and range from photophobia to retro-orbital pain and conjunctivitis [ 95].
